column2: SELECT N.objID AS objID_gal, GT.ra AS ra_gal, GT.dec AS dec_gal, PZ.z AS z_gal, PZ.zErr AS zErr_gal, HS.RA_DEG_J2# AS ra_qso, HS.DEC_DEG_J2# AS dec_qso, HS.NVSS_RM AS RM_qso, HS.NVSS_RM_ERR AS RMErr_qso, HS.SELECTED_REDSHIFT AS z_qso, HS.SELECTED_REDSHIFT_ERR AS zErr_qso into mydb.MyTable from myDB.Hammond_Short HS CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq (HS.RA_DEG_J2#, HS.DEC_DEG_J2#, #) as N
